``` bash
WINEPREFIX=/path/to/prefix  WINEARCH=win64 yabridgectl add /path/to/vsts/
```

> you may get the following error when you try to `sync`: `yabridgectl status/sync prints "Indexed over 100.000 files` this is a bug. see [["Err:module:import_dll Library MFC42u.DLL" Wine Error]] for fix
